<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.180507>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Male (1 – 2, 5) and female (3 – 4) of Stygomomonia manchurica sp. n. 1, dorsum of idiosoma; 2, venter of idiosoma; 3, venter of idiosoma; 4, pedipalp; 5, distal segments of I – L. Scale bars = 50 μm for Figs. 1, 2, 3, 5; 25 μm for Fig. 4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/180507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.180508>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 7. Deutonymph of Stygomomonia manchurica sp. n. 6, dorsum of idiosoma; 7, venter of idiosoma. Scale bar = 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/180508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

